# SlicedLabs · body · © 2026 SlicedLabs
# sl-wallpaper-cycle — advance the SlicedLabs mark wallpaper to its next
# wheel-gradient frame (awww transition morphs the change; engine-backdrop
# re-feeds the glass shader). Driven by sl-wallpaper-cycle.timer.
[Unit]
Description=SlicedLabs mark wallpaper — next gradient frame

[Service]
Type=oneshot
ExecStart=%h/.local/bin/sl-wallpaper mark --tick
